summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the transfer of land in the I-90 Redevelopment Project area; authorizing the acceptance of the deed to I-90 Parcel 37 from the State of Washington, Department of Transportation; authorizing the sale of approximately 1.8 acres of such land to HomeSight for development of housing for sale to first-time home buyers; authorizing a contract for sale of land and deeds; and ratifying and confirming prior acts.
committee: Health, Human Services, Education and Libraries
